long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SafeLink is an extension that detects and highlights potentially malicious links on a webpage. The detected links are rated on a scale of five different factors and given a score that would determine if it is malicious or not. The non-malicious links would appear as usual while the malicious links will appear as highlighted.
